item.description: #introduction: I'm a software developer from #Indianapolis. I mostly write #Scala and #fp. I'm a contributor to #Typelevel and co-founder of #http4s. I nerd out over #Emacs and #Nix. Also enjoy #bbq and freshwater #fishkeeping. I have a #dachshund and a #coonhound and a tuxedo #cat. A couple kids, too, but the pets get more clicks. Pronouns are he/him. Go Hoosiers. #GoIU #iufb #iubb #iums
